Dear OPAR-User,

you have created a repository that you can integrate in your OTRS Package Manager.
To integrate the repository you can add the following data in the SysConfig option
Package::RepositoryList in group "Framework" and subgroup "Core::Package":

Key: <%= URL %>/repo/<%= REPO_ID %>/file?file=
Value: [OPAR] My Repository

You can add and remove packages from your repository at

<%= URL %>/repo/<%= REPO_ID %>/manage

Yours,
OPAR-Team
